itle\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"WP Translation Day 2021: Participe do dia internacional de tradu√ß√£o do WordPress no Brasil!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://br.wordpress.org/2021/09/14/wp-translation-day-2021/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://br.wordpress.org/2021/09/14/wp-translation-day-2021/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 14 Sep 2021 21:51:51 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Meetups\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Traducao\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://br.wordpress.org/?p=2337\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:321:\"Todo ano, a comunidade internacional do WordPress se re√∫ne para celebrar a tradu√ß√£o do WP. A comunidade brasileira sempre foi parte integrante do evento e em 2021 n√£o ser√° diferente: entre os dias 17 e 18 de setembro teremos 24 horas de evento. Venha ajudar a traduzir seu tema ou plugin favorito! O que √© [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Felipe Elia\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2850:\"<figure class=\"wp-block-post-featured-image\"><img width=\"1440\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://br.wordpress.org/files/2021/09/image.png\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://br.wordpress.org/files/2021/09/image.png 1440w, https://br.wordpress.org/files/2021/09/image-300x188.png 300w, https://br.wordpress.org/files/2021/09/image-1024x640.png 1024w, https://br.wordpress.org/files/2021/09/image-768x480.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\" /></figure>\n\n\n<p>Todo ano, a comunidade internacional do WordPress se re√∫ne para celebrar a tradu√ß√£o do WP. A comunidade brasileira sempre foi parte integrante do evento e em 2021 n√£o ser√° diferente: <strong>entre os dias 17 e 18 de setembro</strong> teremos 24 horas de evento. Venha ajudar a traduzir seu tema ou plugin favorito!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>O que √© o WordPress Translation Day?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A tradu√ß√£o do WP, seus plugins e temas √© um esfor√ßo cont√≠nuo durante todo o ano. O WP Translation Day √© um evento organizado tanto pela comunidade internacional, que este ano decidiu por um m√™s inteiro de evento, quanto pelas comunidades locais.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Durante o evento n√≥s criamos novas tradu√ß√µes, revisamos antigas, conversamos sobre o processo geral de tradu√ß√£o e tiramos qualquer d√∫vida que os participantes possam ter.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>O evento √© para pessoas de todos os n√≠veis de conhecimento. A comunidade WordPress segue √† risca seu <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://br.wordpress.org/team/wptd2021/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://br.wordpress.org/team/wptd2021/\" target=\"_blank\">c√≥digo de conduta</a>, ent√£o espere um ambiente receptivo, familiar e descontra√≠do <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.1.0/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"üôÇ\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Quem pode participar?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>O evento √© gratuito e aberto a todos. Para participar √© simples, s√≥ √© preciso:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://login.wordpress.org/register\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://login.wordpress.org/register\" target=\"_blank\">Criar um perfil no WordPress.org</a> para criar suas tradu√ß√µes</li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://br.wordpress.org/team/handbook/comunidade-no-slack/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://br.wordpress.org/team/handbook/comunidade-no-slack/\" target=\"_blank\">Entrar no slack da comunidade WP Brasil</a></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Durante o evento n√≥s tamb√©m teremos confer√™ncias no Zoom.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Qual √© a programa√ß√£o do evento?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Para acessar a programa√ß√£o do evento e ver mais detalhes do que estamos planejando acesse <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://br.wordpress.org/team/wptd2021/\" target=\"_blank\">https://br.wordpress.org/team/wptd2021/</a>. A gente se v√™ dia 17!</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://br.wordpress.org/2021/09/14/wp-translation-day-2021/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"WordPress 5.8.1 ‚Äì Atualiza√ß√£o de manuten√ß√£o e seguran√ßa\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"https://br.wordpress.org/2021/09/09/wordpress-5-8-1-atualizacao-de-manutencao-e-seguranca/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 09 Sep 2021 11:58:40 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Lan√ßamentos\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"5.8\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://br.wordpress.org/?p=2327\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:377:\"O WordPress 5.8.1 j√° est√° dispon√≠vel! Esta vers√£o de manuten√ß√£o e seguran√ßa apresenta 60 corre√ß√µes de erros, al√©m de tr√™s corre√ß√µes de seguran√ßa. Como este √© um lan√ßamento de seguran√ßa, √© recomend√°vel que voc√™ atualize seus sites imediatamente. Todas as vers√µes desde o WordPress 5.4 tamb√©m foram atualizadas. O WordPress 5.8.1 √© uma vers√£o de [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Andre Ribeiro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8948:\"\n<p>O WordPress 5.8.1 j√° est√° dispon√≠vel!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Esta vers√£o de manuten√ß√£o e seguran√ßa apresenta <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?milestone=5.8.1&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=milestone&amp;col=owner&amp;col=type&amp;col=status&amp;col=priority&amp;order=priority\">60 corre√ß√µes de erros</a>, al√©m de tr√™s corre√ß√µes de seguran√ßa. Como este √© um <strong>lan√ßamento de seguran√ßa</strong>, √© recomend√°vel que voc√™ atualize seus sites imediatamente. Todas as vers√µes desde o WordPress 5.4 tamb√©m foram atualizadas.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>O WordPress 5.8.1 √© uma vers√£o de seguran√ßa e manuten√ß√£o de ciclo curto. O pr√≥ximo lan√ßamento principal ser√° a <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/5-9/\">vers√£o 5.9</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Voc√™ pode baixar o WordPress 5.8.1 em WordPress.org ou visite seu Painel ‚Üí Atualiza√ß√µes e clique em Atualizar agora.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Se voc√™ tiver sites que suportam atualiza√ß√µes autom√°ticas em segundo plano, eles j√° iniciaram o processo de atualiza√ß√£o.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Corre√ß√µes de seguran√ßa</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>3 problemas de seguran√ßa afetam as vers√µes do WordPress entre 5.4 e 5.8. Se voc√™ ainda n√£o atualizou para 5.8, todas as vers√µes do WordPress desde 5.4 tamb√©m foram atualizadas para corrigir os seguintes problemas de seguran√ßa:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Agradecemos a <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mdawaffe/\">@mdawaffe</a>, membro da equipe de seguran√ßa do WordPress, por seu trabalho corrigindo uma vulnerabilidade de exposi√ß√£o de dados na API REST.</li><li>Agradecemos a Micha≈Ç Bentkowski, da Securitum, por relatar uma vulnerabilidade de XSS no editor de blocos.</li><li>Para incorporar as corre√ß√µes de seguran√ßa lan√ßadas pela equipe da biblioteca Lodash, sua vers√£o foi atualizada para 4.17.21 em cada vers√£o do WordPress.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Al√©m desses problemas, a equipe de seguran√ßa gostaria de agradecer √†s seguintes pessoas por relatar vulnerabilidades durante o per√≠odo de teste beta do WordPress 5.8, permitindo que elas fossem corrigidas antes do lan√ßamento:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Agradecemos a <a href=\"https://evanricafort.com/\">Evan Ricafort</a> por relatar uma vulnerabilidade XSS no editor de blocos descoberta durante o per√≠odo beta da vers√£o 5.8.</li><li>Agradecemos a <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stevehenty/\">Steve Henty</a> por relatar um problema de escalonamento de privil√©gios no editor de blocos.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Agradecemos tamb√©m a todos os colaboradores por divulgarem as vulnerabilidades em particular. Isso deu √† equipe de seguran√ßa do WordPress tempo para corrigir as vulnerabilidades antes que os sites do WordPress pudessem ser atacados.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Para obter mais informa√ß√µes, navegue na <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?milestone=5.8.1&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=milestone&amp;col=owner&amp;col=type&amp;col=status&amp;col=priority&amp;order=priority\">lista completa de altera√ß√µes no Trac</a> ou<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/wordpress-version/version-5-8-1/\"> verifique a p√°gina de documenta√ß√£o do HelpHub da vers√£o 5.8.1</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Agradecimentos</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A vers√£o 5.8.1 foi liderada por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/desrosj/\">Jonathan Desrosiers</a> e <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/circlecube/\">Evan Mullins</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Al√©m dos pesquisadores de seguran√ßa e membros do esquadr√£o de lan√ßamento mencionados acima, agradecemos a todos que ajudaram a fazer o WordPress 5.8.1 acontecer:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/2linctools/\">2linctools</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zieladam/\">Adam Zielinski</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/schlessera/\">Alain Schlesser</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ajlende/\">Alex Lende</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alexstine/\">alexstine</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/algala/\">AlGala</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/oandregal/\">Andr√©</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/andraganescu/\">Andrei Draganescu</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/azaozz/\">Andrew Ozz</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ankitmaru/\">Ankit Panchal</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/antpb/\">Anthony Burchell</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/antonvlasenko/\">Anton Vlasenko</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aristath/\">Ari Stathopoulos</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ribaricplusplus/\">Bruno Ribaric</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/poena/\">Carolina Nymark</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/daisyo/\">Daisy Olsen</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/talldanwp/\">Daniel Richards</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dariak/\">Daria</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davidanderson/\">David Anderson</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davidbinda/\">David Bi≈àovec</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dlh/\">David Herrera</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ocean90/\">Dominik Schilling</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ellatrix/\">Ella van¬†Durpe</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/enchiridion/\">Enchiridion</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/circlecube/\">Evan Mullins</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/garyj/\">Gary Jones</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mamaduka/\">George Mamadashvili</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gziolo/\">Greg Zi√≥≈Çkowski</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/priethor/\">H√©ctor Prieto</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ianmjones/\">ianmjones</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/audrasjb/\">Jb Audras</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jblz/\">Jeff Bowen</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joedolson/\">Joe Dolson</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joen/\">Joen A.</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/johnbillion/\">John Blackbourn</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/desrosj/\">Jonathan Desrosiers</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/juanmaguitar/\">JuanMa Garrido</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jrf/\">Juliette Reinders Folmer</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kevin940726/\">Kai Hao</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kapilpaul/\">Kapil Paul</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gwwar/\">Kerry Liu</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kevinfodness/\">Kevin Fodness</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mkaz/\">Marcus Kazmierczak</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mark-k/\">Mark-k</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mhuntdesign/\">Matt</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mdawaffe/\">Michael Adams (mdawaffe)</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mikeschroder/\">Mike Schroder</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/moch11/\">moch11</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mukesh27/\">Mukesh Panchal</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ntsekouras/\">Nik Tsekouras</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/paaljoachim/\">Paal Joachim Romdahl</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/swissspidy/\">Pascal Birchler</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pbearne/\">Paul Bearne</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pbiron/\">Paul Biron</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/peterwilsoncc/\">Peter Wilson</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/walbo/\">Petter Walb√∏ Johnsg√•rd</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/radixweb/\">Radixweb</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rtm909/\">Rahul Mehta</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ramonopoly/\">ramonopoly</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ravipatel/\">ravipatel</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/youknowriad/\">Riad Benguella</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/noisysocks/\">Robert Anderson</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kreppar/\">Rodrigo Arias</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sanketchodavadiya/\">Sanket Chodavadiya</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sergeybiryukov/\">Sergey Biryukov</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sabernhardt/\">Stephen Bernhardt</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/netweb/\">Stephen Edgar</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stevehenty/\">Steve Henty</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/terraling/\">terraling</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/timothyblynjacobs/\">Timothy Jacobs</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tmatsuur/\">tmatsuur</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tobiasbg/\">TobiasBg</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hellofromTonya/\">Tonya Mork</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/toro_unit/\">Toro_Unit (Hiroshi Urabe)</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vladytimy/\">Vlad T</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wb1234/\">wb1234</a> e <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wfmattr/\">WFMattR</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"WordPress 5.8 Tatum\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://br.wordpress.org/2021/07/20/wordpress-5-8-tatum/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";